{
  "stem": "8786.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But in our town, it came Hanukkah time, each of the children had his own group.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Two have a little fun, or play around, or play a little cards.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And our-- our family was a special one, because in every room-- we had about seven rooms.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "In each room, there was my sister's friends, and my other sister's friends, and my father's friends, and the boys' friends.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "We had groups of people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And everybody had beautiful fun, what you call.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And it wasn't a-- playing cards for the money.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "It was just the plain-- very nice social gathering.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "That remains with me for-- for as long as I live.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "It was beautiful, because my father was a wonderful sense of humor.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And he was going from room to room, and the youngsters were-- they were just-- they loved to hear his remarks and stories.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The name of the town was Tornala.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's a town today in Slovakia in the southern part of Slovakia.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's called Tornala-- T-O-R-N-A-L-A.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About my drawing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, I was a-- I knew how to draw.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, all my sisters, they all-- they were all doing beautiful, beautiful handwriting and very nice drawing.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Singing was a hobby of mine since I was born.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I still do it if I have a chance or if they call up on me.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was maybe 13 years old when the cantor of the town, who had a beautiful, beautiful voice-- and he said it to me those days.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was helping him in his services.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And as a reward, it came Simchat Torah, they usually-- [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] he bought-- he bought a-- the honor to for me that I should perform in the big synagogue.",
      "word_count": 32
    }
  ],
